Case #0071304

Statement of Evo Lensik regarding his experiences during the construction of a house on hilltop road Oxford.

…

Remember that during these launch weeks we need as many reviews and subscriptions as possible in order to get the attention we need to climb up the podcast charts. Every time you recommend our work you help us make more!

For the duration of launch we will be releasing three episodes a week instead of our normal weekly release schedule. We hope you enjoy the extra terror…

Like what you’re hearing? Let us know:

Tweet us at @theRustyQuill, drop us an email at mail@RustyQuill.com or comment on our dedicated Forums available at www.RustyQuill.com.
